name: Exuberance No. 2
description:
Extend upward to the stars and reach for the celestial heavens; Exuberance No. 2 Cobalt Blue and Green create cosmic kinetic energy. This captivating painting pulsates in variations of Cobalt Blue and Green with a touch of Deep Cadmium Orange.

Exuberance No. 2 is a one-of-a-kind artistic collaboration that intertwines Tery Spataro's flower photographs with the artificial intelligence of Playform.io to give life to this transfixing creation.

Exuberance No. 2 is accompanied by a physical print on a 15.7"x15.7" canvas.
